Recommends:
 ffmpeg,
Description: Ultimate camera streaming application
 go2rtc is a zero-dependency camera streaming application with support for
 dozens of formats and protocols. It provides zero-delay streaming for many
 supported protocols with the lowest possible latency.
 .
 Features include streaming from RTSP, WebRTC, ONVIF, HomeKit, RTMP, HLS,
 and many more protocols; on-the-fly transcoding via FFmpeg when necessary;
 two-way audio support; and a built-in web interface for configuration and
 monitoring.
 .
 Default ports: 1984 (API/WebUI), 8554 (RTSP), 8555 (WebRTC).
